      "content": "it's not just one day though. it's like... everything i do just makes things harder for them. i look at them and i just feel this massive weight. it feels like i'm just a shadow in their lives, a constant reminder of what they're missing out on. if i wasn't here, they could actually have a chance at a real, happy life without my mess holding them back.",
